OL,1,MA]G  Aftercare: Goujon Palm        Px}0
OL,2,                       k                
OL,3,                                  Q "###
OL,4,C Congratulations on your permanent bond
OL,5,C with the Leader. Follow these Ministry
OL,6,C of Harmony guildelines to ensure      
OL,7,C purity of the face-palm image.        
OL,9,  DO NOT SCRUB:FThe laser charred dermis
OL,10,F is a badge of honour. Scrubbing       
OL,11,F constitutes defacing a State Icon.    
OL,13,  VISIBILIY:FKeep the palm exposed      
OL,14,F during the National Anthem.           
OL,15,F Concealment of the Leader's face is a 
OL,16,F Class 4 Enforcement Offence.          
OL,18,  SWELLING:FMinor blistering is a sign  
OL,19,F of "Patriotic Heat". Apply Goujon-    
OL,20,F Brand Zinc Paste from your local      
OL,21,F Commissary.                           
OL,22,  FM"My hand burns with His love!"      
OL,24,ANext  BDuties   CReporting   FPurity   
